{"tid":323834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「巴打入」A0正常樣男仔","createTime":"2017-07-16T02:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T07:52:36.000Z","uid":28569,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0b10353477f119730666ce19dd3da371d8c8f3","tid":323834,"uid":28569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"點解我遇唔到一個自己岩既女仔<br />\n番工番學身邊都有女性<br />\n但完全睇唔上眼<br />\n見到出邊咁多靚女都比人溝晒<br />\n就會覺得自己好似無機會出pool咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己本身條件唔差 有幾條女追過 但因為個樣唔岩而唔同佢地一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時先可以識到個我覺得岩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打同我差唔多情況 或者有無絲打想講兩句<br />\n<br />\n利申 外協會員"},{"pid":"f2d0eb6ae77bb56b5629bf3d08262afe011933dc","tid":323834,"uid":83531,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"正常樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70741503963d527bd3d1f8c362cffcc7a9bc642","tid":323834,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:55:43.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫正常樣&hellip;？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c72c3a699b6d73d54f558c4b6671ae8531c77b","tid":323834,"uid":9460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:55:44.000Z","msg":"因為你唔係正常樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eeb1eb0da55134c3c176a90a6fcc06e3c45f772","tid":323834,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":