if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a624397a02b8a1ad1764e8370cad73dbf63d3b7","tid":323834,"uid":109567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"正常樣又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你都識講正常樣 姐係你格黎左右都一大堆啦<br />\n普通樣既女仔你又唔受 靚女就自然多人追架啦<br />\n<br />\n拿 先唔講型撚/人生勝利組<br />\n你左邊果個可能正常樣 但米8大隻仔<br />\n你右邊果個可能正常樣 但識打扮斯文仔仲識撚結他<br />\n你後面果個可能又正常樣 但人地識講野又識搞氣氛 食女無數<br />\n<br />\n咁你有咩優點可以吸引到靚女先？"},{"pid":"32c8c7656c05c437175c2995f61670a106e633f2","tid":323834,"uid":34503,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"連登仔口中正常樣：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/l39Zf63Le193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fl39Zf63Le193.jpg&h=46bfe803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Screen-Shot-2016-12-31-at-5.34.54-PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2FScreen-Shot-2016-12-31-at-5.34.54-PM.jpg&h=6b4d4056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女"},{"pid":"8732e8d2c9504bb0fc2dac779f0ba831f9edddcf","tid":323834,"uid":126681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:18:37.000Z","msg":"自貼左先啦 ，唔明咩係正常樣"},{"pid":"5731aeca57b32e04802d08ba12a91e660de33f3b","tid":323834,"uid":5733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"比d慨念圖睇過"},{"pid":"9d23625287e9cc9c969293ff36dec31695efd79f","tid":323834,"uid":28569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你係唔係比人收兵就當比人追呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到明叫我比機會佢仲算唔算收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5236835ecea33111b8f86e1